  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  texts:
  - Welcome to your first fight we are the Akatsuki!
  - "Your courage is admirable\u2026 but it won\u2019t save you."
  - "Stand your ground if you wish\u2026 the Akatsuki do not hold back."
  - "Few survive their first encounter with us\u2026 let\u2019s see if you\u2019re
    different."
  - "Remember this moment\u2026 it\u2019s the last calm before the fight."
  - "Let\u2019s see if your strength matches your confidence."
